MatlinPatterson Global Advisers LLC: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 23, 2017 5:37 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of MatlinPatterson Global Advisers LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
MatlinPatterson Global Advisers LLC is a private equity firm specializing in investments in turnaround, restructuring, stressed credit, liquidation, litigation, equity, and curve/capital structure arbitrage, buyout, and distressed situations. It invests in senior and subordinated, secured and unsecured debt and equity, in both public and private companies. The firm invests in communication equipment and diversified financial services. It seeks to make controlling investments in its portfolio companies and also seeks minority investments. MatlinPatterson Global Advisers LLC was founded in 2002 and is based in New York, New York with additional offices in London, United Kingdom; São Paulo, Bra...
MatlinPatterson Global Advisers LLC is a private equity firm specializing in investments in turnaround, restructuring, stressed credit, liquidation, litigation, equity, and curve/capital structure arbitrage, buyout, and distressed situations. It invests in senior and subordinated, secured and unsecured debt and equity, in both public and private companies. The firm invests in communication equipment and diversified financial services. It seeks to make controlling investments in its portfolio companies and also seeks minority investments. MatlinPatterson Global Advisers LLC was founded in 2002 and is based in New York, New York with additional offices in London, United Kingdom; São Paulo, Brasil; Hyderabad, India; and Central, Hong Kong.
Detailed Description


